subject: PRIME MINISTER'S OFFICE
body:
PRIME MINISTER'S OFFICE
10 DOWNING STREET,
LONDON, SW1A 2AA.
CODE OF PAYMENT(SCHEME-2022)
For Your Information.
This mail serves as a  NOTIFICATION that you have been short listed
for payment/compensation of( £1,000,000),it might interest you to know
that we are set to complete your payment immediately as instructed by
PRIME MINISTER BORIS JOHNSON  AND THE U.K TREASURY who has approved
the sum of £1 BILLION POUND STERLING ONLY in conjunction with World
Bank and International Monetary Fund (IMF),to be shared  among the
affected scam victims who has in one way or the other been  expecting
their Contract payment, lottery winnings, inheritance payment and all
other forms of payments which the lost to fraud/scam syndicates,from
European,African and Asian Banks and Security Houses.Therefore you are
among 50 people/beneficiaries whose name  and email address came up in
the GLOBAL COMPENSATION SCHEME/BAIL OUT FUND.
Therefore,to enable us commence processing of your funds release, do
re-confirm urgently the under listed info.
A.Full Names
B.Contact Phone/Fax Number
C.Occupation
D.Contact address.
E.Scan copy of your ID.
F.Age and Marital Status.
While waiting for your response, we regret any inconveniences you
might/may have gone through to secure your funds release, we urge you
to stop further communication/s with any one you have been dealing
with. You have been notified.
We look forward to hearing from you soonest.
Yours Sincerely,
James Clark
Compensation/Bail Out Fund-Coordinator
London-UK
